.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, reading, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, egyptian, mexican
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the egyptian##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | dancing   | reading | board-games | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Nationality   | canadian | chinese   | egyptian    | mexican   |

