1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the firefighter##1
3. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
