4. the bolivar-smoker is between the pilot and the polish##2
5. the pilot is the argentine##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the dancer##3

