3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the van and the person drinking water##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage      | water      | sprite     | juice | coffee |
| Birthday   | may    | july    | march   | february |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter | van   | car    |

