4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | almond-milk | lemonade  |
| Food          | kale          | asparagus | mango       | kiwi      |
| Color   | turquise     | amber    | grey     | aquamarine |

